  <title>SET SCOPEBOTTOM 命令</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Commands</keyword>
    <keyword>Databases</keyword>
    <keyword>Index/order</keyword>
    <keyword>Scoping key values</keyword>
    <keyword>SET SCOPEBOTTOM command</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">SET SCOPEBOTTOM 命令</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><snippet src="__CommandInclude" inline="false"/></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading1">用途</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">更改控制 order 中键值范围的下边界。</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading1">语法</para>
    <para styleclass="Code with box">SET SCOPEBOTTOM TO [&lt;uNewBottom&gt;]</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading1">描述</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">SET SCOPEBOTTOM 与 &lt;uNewBottom&gt; 参数一起使用时，功能等同于 OrdScope(1, &lt;uNewBottom&gt;)。 SET SCOPEBOTTOM 不带参数时，功能等同于 OrdScope(1, NIL)。 </para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><snippet src="__IncludeLibRt" inline="false"/></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading1">参见</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="html\M_XSharp_RT_Functions_OrdScope.htm" domain="XSharpRef.chm">OrdScope()</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
  </body>
